- This is terrifying.

198
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,400
- No.
- How can this be?

199
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:15,480
Please lower your voice. No, this...

200
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,880
This is

201
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:19,240
chili powder.

202
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,920
And this is cumin.

203
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,680
