205
00:10:24,640 --> 00:10:25,620
Please try it.

206
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:27,380
I know all that.

207
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,200
This stuff is so dirty.

208
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,740
