209
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:31,960
- Oh, my.
- No.

210
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,720
- Stop saying that.
- How can this be food?

211
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,440
I prepared it for you.

212
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,780
Of course, it's food.

213
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:39,040
Dr. Sun, even if you've helped my family,

214
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:40,480
