222
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,660
- Smashed it?
- I didn't.

223
00:10:51,660 --> 00:10:52,680
- Oh, my.
- I didn't.

224
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:53,880
You dropped it yourself.

225
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,160
Did you throw it?

226
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:56,720
I'm telling you.

227
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,600
If you keep this up,

228
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,840
I'll call the police.

229
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,380
