245
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,860
Xia.

246
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:27,760
Xia.

247
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,220
Stop playing basketball.

248
00:11:29,560 --> 00:11:30,900
